      "span_text": "Additional recombinant expression constructs included the following: pLP-mCh vector (CMV promoter); pLP-mCh-mTomo1 (mouse); pDNR-mTomo1-⌬CT, that is Tomo1 with deletion of C-terminal SNARE domain residues 1067-1131 ; pCDNA CAPTEV-CT containing mTomo1 (rat; Invitrogen vector); and pLenti (synapsin promoter) containing YFP-mTomo1  ; pcDNA3.1-Cdk5 (D144N), a dominant negative Cdk5 mutant (Shuang et al., 1998) ."
